Practical no.9
Aim : Email Forensics 

Step 1 :Open Forensic Toolkit(ftk181.exe) and click on “Start a new case”

Step 2 : Fill the form new case >  next.

Step 3 : fill forensic examiner information >  next.

Step 4 : Select HTML file listing, Data Carve, Registry Reports > next.

Step 7:  click on Add evidence > Individual file > continue.
         Continue karne ke baad add file file karneka joh (cf_software > ftk181 > Jim_shu's.pst [add this file])

Step 8 : Fill the evidence form > next > finish.
          Let the process complete.

Step 9 : select “From E-mail”

Step 10 : Select any message and Export it as a file
Make sure to check “Export HTML view if available” and Click on OK. 

Step 11 : Deleted Message is recovered at the specified location

Step 12 : Click on .html file, it will get open in the Browser showing the content of the email. 
